				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Vxed! HELP!<a name="60907"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Sep 8 04 1:31 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>We used to be able to Deftdance tank the name at the end while the Charmed pet owned it.  But I haven't been back to Vxed since the change a few months back, so I don't know if that's still possible.
<br />

<br />
Basically, our only use there is to pull and play CHA for the tank so DI fires...
<br />

<br />
Crowd Control isn't needed as a Chanter is garunteed to be there, and they don't need us to Mez their pet when Charm breaks since it will be Snared.  Our Haste and Overhaste songs are near pointless as the pet does all the real damage.  And Resists are not a real issue.  So we're left with pulling, basically.
<br />

<br />
Best thing to have in Vxed is a Necromancer.  Nothing worse than having the Cleric go down and every dieing except the Bard.  But with a Necro, you are back in business.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
