				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Vxed! HELP!<a name="60914"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Sep 8 04 2:16 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>We won Vxed a couple of days ago with a SK (time/EP geared), warrior (EP geared), boxed shaman, cleric, ranger, bard (me).
<br />

<br />
There's no real reason to rush here, we stayed at the zonein for a while and killed there, after about 30 mobs we started proceeding to the Stonespiritist. I was pulling, except when we got to the room with Stonespiritist, we found it to be less painful to have the SK FD pull that room due to the casting snakes. Usually we only had 1 mob in camp, sometimes 2, at one hectic moment 4. Warrior tanked all the way thru, SK offtanked a bit when we had 4 in camp. We also killed the named pooka who dropped greaves for the cleric. You don't need to mess with charmed pets or suchlike, bring a good solid group that knows what they're doing and it should be easy. You don't have to kill any named to get the flag, just spawn the spiritist and get to her.
<br />

<br />
We even spawned her yesterday just doing exp at zonein and helped a few guildies to get their Vxed flag with selos+kazumis run up to the spiritist.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
