				<td><img src="/skins/default/images/user_IsOffline.gif" alt="Flayre is not online. Last active: 1/20/2005 5:27:51 PM" border="0" />&nbsp;<a class="SmallBoldText" href="/User/UserProfile.aspx?UserName=Flayre">Flayre</a><br></td>
