				<td colspan="2"><span>-Vxed I do not melee.
<br />
-I keep my drum and cha and singing gear equipped.
<br />
-I pull with HoS, and then keep HoS going on the pulled mob while killing it.  I also twist mana and focus while the target is being killed.
<br />
-I keep the chanters pet targeted at all times that I am not pulling (well except when singing HoS in twist I switch back for cast), and then just hang back singing keeping an eye on the pet and handling any CC that needs to be done.
<br />

<br />
It can get a little tricky pulling and CCing while keeping tabs on the pet... but not hard.  If you have someone else who can pull and then you can keep full-time tabs on the chanter pet and CC you can almost run through vxed, lol;  especially if the pet has toys and haste.
<br />

<br />
Vxed and tipt with chanter pets are soooo fun.</span></td>
